msgid "<b>Access</b> (Art. 15 of the GDPR): you have the right to obtain confirmation as to whether we process your personal data, as well as information about how we process it. You can also request a copy of your personal data, for which we may charge you a reasonable fee based on administrative costs. In order to exercise your right of access, contact us at"
msgstr "<b>Pravo na pristup</b> (Čl. 15 GDPR-a): imate pravo dobiti potvrdu obrađuju li se Vaši osobni podatci i na koji način. Možete zatražiti kopiju Vaših osobnih podataka, za koju smijemo naplatiti razumnu naknadu temeljenu na administrativnim troškovima. Kako biste ostvarili svoje pravo pristupa, javite nam se na"

msgid "<b>Rectification</b> (Art. 16 of the GDPR): if your personal data that we process are incomplete or inaccurate, you have the right to request rectification of such data without undue delay. In order to exercise your right to rectification, contact us at"
msgstr "<b>Pravo na ispravak</b> (Čl. 16 GDPR-a): ako su Vaši osobni podatci koje obrađujemo nepotpuni ili netočni, imate pravo zatražiti ispravak podataka bez nepotrebnog odgađanja. Kako biste ostvarili svoje pravo na ispravak, javite nam se na"

msgid "<b>Right to object</b> (Art. 21 of the GDPR): if you did not consent to the processing, or if it is not necessary to comply with a legal obligation, you may always object to it, in which case we shall no longer process your data."
msgstr "<b>Pravo na prigovor</b> (Čl. 21 GDPR-a): "ako niste dali privolu za obradu, ili ako nije potrebno pridržavati se zakonske obveze, uvijek možete uložiti prigovor, te u tom slučaju nećemo dalje obrađivati Vaše podatke."     

msgid "Moreover, you have the right to"
msgstr "Nadalje, imate pravo"

msgid "The withdrawal of consent will not affect the lawfulness of processing based on consent before its withdrawal."
msgstr "Povlačenje privole neće utjecati na zakonitost obrade na temelju pristanka danog prije njezinog povlačenja."

msgid "we value your privacy and process your data in compliance with the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)."
msgstr "cijenimo Vašu privatnost i obrađujemo Vaše podatke u skladu s EU-ovom Općom uredbom o zaštiti podataka (GDPR)."

